race.comment: NOLAN BALE (5) doesn't win out of turn. Better run when finding the frame last time though, finishing third (22.98) at Ballarat. Must be included in calculations. DECORATED (1) comes off an average effort last start when seventh at Bendigo over 425m behind Frank Grimes (25.71) in a Grade 5. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. One of the better chances. QUANTUM MASTER (2) can sneak into the finish with the right run. Something for the Multiples: TASTE OF HELL (4)
